original_title: 初音ミクシンフォニー ~ Miku Symphony 2018 - 2019 ~
overview: A 2-day live concert from Crypton Future Media and the sequel to the Miku Symphony 2016 and 2017 concerts. This is the second official Miku Symphony to feature all Crypton characters, the first being the 2017 Miku Symphony. It also celebrates the 10th anniversaries of Megurine Luka, Kasane Teto, and Snow Miku.
title: Hatsune Miku Symphony 2018-2019 Orchestral Live
